      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DETECTIVE (7) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (20.41) at this track in a Maiden. Lines up from box 7 for the first time. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. ANTI VENOM (1) has been in the minor money at both career runs, the latest finishing second (20.39) at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance. HELLO GEMINI (8) is on debut without trialling for this. Can measure up. MANGO BEACH (4) makes debut for the Cameron Scott kennel. Start all important from the squeeze box. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
